Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya... let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We can't start until we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:27.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai, who you wanted to play, is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you'll notice or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Sai is in the games I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll become just as good as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and play against you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally get to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't played you since the third\Nboard match in the Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two years and four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it was a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I will show you my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:22.31,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(345,115)}The Seventy-Fourth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:22.31,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Forever Inside You
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:29.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If you're going to respond with another\NKakari, I'll do a low pincer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll spread the fight across the board and\Nwe'll enter a kill-or-be killed fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I finally got the chance to play against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's been since the game in the Go tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No, Sai played the first half of that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:05.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya, this is the first real game between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's a daring pincer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll break out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So that's how you want to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I have to do a Suberi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He responded correctly in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's just as good as a high-dan pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This... this is a Kifu from a game\NShindou played, Mr. Yun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I happened to see him when he\Nwas playing a game in a Go salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:34.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Both Black and White are good enough to be pros...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But White especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun is White. Black is a Korean\Nkenkyuusei, Hong Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially considering how disappointed you\Nwere after playing him in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how good he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's me. How did the pro exams turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.67,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.43,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been decided? All three?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are no playoffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Waya-kun beat Fukui-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.81,Background,,0,0,0,,and Shindou beat Ochi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always looking up, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you probably don't know about\Nthe scary guy beneath you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not really beneath you,\Nbut immediately behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You and he are the two who will be threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He just became a pro this year.\NHis name is Shindou Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should watch out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:49.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know how strong you were all this time,\Nand you're just as strong as I had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:56.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it. You\Nwill become my lifelong rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.79,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes, good work.
