Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:01.67,Background,,0,0,0,,How do you pronounce this Korean child's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "kou" from "kouzui" (kouzui is\Nflood) so would it be Hong? Hong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The child who beat Kim Kang Il? It's Su-Young.\NHis name is Hong Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:19.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Hong Su-Young, 14. Yet another\Nincredible new player for Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixteen year old Ko Young Ha is setting the\Nrecord for the longest winning streak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The young players are really good in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Su-Young, Ko Young Ha... I wonder\Nif they're the ones who will be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a rumor right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but there may be a Japan, China,\NKorea Junior Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a corporation is trying to sponsor\Na team tournament between pros
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from Japan, China, and Korea under the age of 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan, China, Korea Junior Tournament!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the age of 18!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one of that age in Japan who\Ncan go up against China and Korea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Touya Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But Touya-kun isn't enough by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that boy, Ochi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochi-kun... he still hasn't lost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's 14. That's an impressive age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt he can do much\Nagainst China and Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun is the only one we can really count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.23,Background,,0,0,0,,There's Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:24.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I saw a glimmer of Sai in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The other person that I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,coming in and out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That shadow I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've always been chasing after...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou? The kid who didn't\Nshow up to his matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.77,Background,,0,0,0,,Do you mean him, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe he has just as much\Npotential as Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People like Touya Kouyou, Kuwabara\NHoninbou, and Ogata Jyudan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,have been interested in him for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about how Master\NTouya requested to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,play Shindou-kun for the new\Nfirst-dan series game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the game itself was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But strangely, Master Kuwabara\Nand the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,did not change their opinion of\NShindou-kun because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:32.00,Background,,0,0,0,,And ever since I learned that Touya-kun\Nsees Shindou-kun as a rival,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become one of the people who\Nis counting on Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun does!? It would\Nbe great if that were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I've heard of a rumor that Master\NKuwabara thinks highly of Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Kurata-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The match between Shindou\Nand Touya is this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...the other day. Maybe Kurata-san too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Even Kurata-kun thinks highly of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How has he done since he started\Ncoming to his matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He played eight games and won them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great. I hope the young people\Nkeep replacing the top players like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, the old folks won't give up that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master Ogata has already cut into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.40,Background,,0,0,0,,We have Kurata-kun, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:41.86,Background,,0,0,0,,No, it's about Touya-kun. He will surpass\NMaster Ogata and Master Kurata!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.62,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, the match between Touya-kun and\NShindou-kun is going on today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I get so excited thinking about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.81,Background,,0,0,0,,We have Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:21.48,Background,,0,0,0,,And with Ochi-kun and Waya-kun and the\Nothers thrown in, they form a new wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The strength of youth! The\Narrival of the next generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with Touya-kun in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear Shindou-kun is just\Nas good as Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can finally aim for the world! It'll be\Na comeback for Japan! Right, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great. Our sales would improve\Na lot if that were to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we have no idea what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:21.38,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\1c&H5A727E&\bord0\shad0\frz8\fscy95\move(412,160,412,488)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.41,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to our talk of dreams now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This game's been moving really quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's a really complex battle going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But he's doing well against Touya despite the difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeki-kun! Wanna go eat together? Meals are no\Ngood unless you have someone to eat with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And Akira never eats during a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go. What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.33,Background,,0,0,0,,A-Ashiwara-san! H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do Touya's students think\Nof Morishita's students?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We stopped the clock after Touya's Katatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I should play on the lower left instead\Nof the conflict at the top right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:21.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll play at the Keima to assault White's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya will definitely connect, so\NI'll just get life on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:33.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The lower left is still too small.\NHow should I attack the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm at a disadvantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No. It's close. I can still play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya, what are you doing about lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go before we run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is he not going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:20.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of Sai from the Internet\Nwhen I was playing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Sai, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shindou Hikaru when we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,someone else inside you!
