Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When White played here at this\Npoint, that was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Black could play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Atari, so White has to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Black moves here, and White loses its eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, White has to protect at this point.
